#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:44
msgid "Deliverability"
msgstr "Entregabilitat"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:46
msgid ""
"A diagnostic check only — nothing here changes how mail is sent. On ordinary "
"hosting (PHP mail(), no SMTP plugin), mail sent from an address that doesn't "
"match your site's own domain, or from a domain with no SPF/DMARC record at "
"all, is increasingly likely to land in spam or be rejected outright by large "
"mailbox providers. If any row below looks wrong, the most reliable fix is "
"installing an SMTP-sending plugin (WP Mail SMTP, Post SMTP, FluentSMTP, and "
"others all work) configured against a real transactional mail provider, and "
"adding SPF/DMARC records for the domain you send from at your DNS host."
msgstr ""
"Només una comprovació de diagnòstic: aquí no es canvia res de com s'envia el "
"correu. En allotjaments habituals (PHP mail(), sense connector SMTP), el "
"correu enviat des d'una adreça que no coincideixi amb el domini del teu "
"lloc, o des d'un domini sense cap registre SPF/DMARC, té cada vegada més "
"probabilitats d'acabar a correu brossa o de ser rebutjat directament pels "
"grans proveïdors de bústies. Si alguna fila de sota sembla incorrecta, la "
"solució més fiable és instal·lar un connector d'enviament SMTP (WP Mail "
"SMTP, Post SMTP, FluentSMTP i altres funcionen) configurat amb un proveïdor "
"real de correu transaccional, i afegir registres SPF/DMARC per al domini des "
"del qual envies al teu proveïdor DNS."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:52
msgid "From identity"
msgstr "Identitat del remitent"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:53
msgid "Domain matches site?"
msgstr "El domini coincideix amb el del lloc?"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:54
msgid "SPF record"
msgstr "Registre SPF"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:55
msgid "DMARC record"
msgstr "Registre DMARC"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:56
msgid "DKIM record"
msgstr "Registre DKIM"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:57
msgid "Spamhaus DBL"
msgstr "Spamhaus DBL"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:75
msgid "SMTP plugin"
msgstr "Connector SMTP"

#. translators: %s: detected plugin name, e.g. "WP Mail SMTP"
#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:82
#, php-format
msgid "Detected: %s"
msgstr "Detectat: %s"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:87
msgid ""
"None of the common SMTP-sending plugins were detected — this site is likely "
"relying on PHP's built-in mail(), which most hosts deliver poorly through."
msgstr ""
"No s'ha detectat cap dels connectors habituals d'enviament SMTP: aquest lloc "
"probablement depèn del mail() integrat de PHP, que la majoria d'allotjaments "
"lliuren amb poca fiabilitat."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:94
msgid ""
"DKIM is best-effort: there's no fixed location for a DKIM record the way SPF "
"and DMARC have, so this only checks a handful of common provider selectors. "
"\"Not found\" here does not mean DKIM isn't configured — only that it isn't "
"under one of the names this check happens to try. If you already know your "
"DKIM is set up correctly (your provider's dashboard confirmed it), trust "
"that over this row."
msgstr ""
"DKIM és de millor esforç: no hi ha una ubicació fixa per a un registre DKIM "
"com sí que hi ha per a SPF i DMARC, així que això només comprova un grapat "
"de selectors comuns de proveïdors. \"No trobat\" aquí no vol dir que DKIM no "
"estigui configurat — només que no és sota cap dels noms que aquesta "
"comprovació prova. Si ja sabeu que el vostre DKIM està configurat "
"correctament (el tauler del vostre proveïdor ho ha confirmat), feu cas "
"d'això abans que d'aquesta fila."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:100
msgid "Send a real test email to:"
msgstr "Envia un correu de prova real a:"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:105
msgid ""
"Sends one plain-text email from the same community identity used for review/"
"vote/vouch mail. Reaching your inbox is a good sign; landing in spam or not "
"arriving at all confirms a real deliverability problem regardless of what "
"the checks above say."
msgstr ""
"Envia un sol correu electrònic en text pla des de la mateixa identitat de la "
"comunitat que s'utilitza per al correu de revisió/votació/aval. Que arribi a "
"la safata d'entrada és un bon senyal; si acaba a correu brossa o no arriba, "
"confirma un problema real d'entregabilitat, independentment del que diguin "
"les comprovacions anteriors."

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:114
msgid "Found"
msgstr "Trobat"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:115
msgid "Not found"
msgstr "No trobat"

#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:116
#: includes/Admin/Dashboards/DeliverabilityCard.php:163
msgid "DNS lookup failed"
