#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:519
msgid ""
"Your membership application/account is still active. To remove this data, "
"use the \"leave the network\" link from any Agnosis email, or ask an "
"administrator."
msgstr ""
"La teva sol·licitud de pertinença/compte encara és activa. Per eliminar "
"aquestes dades, fes servir l’enllaç \"deixar la xarxa\" de qualsevol correu "
"electrònic d’Agnosis, o demana-ho a un administrador."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:539
msgid ""
"Your biography, statement, and portfolio link were erased. Your email "
"address was kept on file — your account is currently banned, and it's the "
"only way this site can continue to enforce that."
msgstr ""
"La teva biografia, declaració i l’enllaç del teu portafolis s’han esborrat. "
"La teva adreça electrònica s’ha conservat — el teu compte està actualment "
"blocat, i és l’única manera que aquest lloc pot continuar aplicant-ho."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:613 includes/Core/Privacy.php:685
msgid "[message removed]"
msgstr "[missatge eliminat]"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:624
msgid ""
"Vouch messages you wrote were redacted. Governance votes you cast were kept "
"as-is — a vote is a community record, not personal data, and removing it "
"would silently change a settled decision."
msgstr ""
"Els missatges d’avals que vas escriure s’han censurat. Els vots de "
"governança que vas emetre s’han conservat tal com eren — un vot és un "
"registre de la comunitat, no una dada personal, i eliminar-lo canviaria "
"silenciosament una decisió ja presa."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:667
msgid ""
"Past newsletter delivery records were anonymized; per-issue delivery counts "
"were kept for statistics."
msgstr ""
"Els registres antics d’entrega del butlletí s’han anonimitzat; els recomptes "
"d’entregues per número s’han conservat per a les estadístiques."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:728
msgid ""
"Transaction (donation/sale) records were kept in full — financial records "
"are subject to a legal retention obligation and are exempt from erasure "
"under GDPR Art. 17(3)(b)."
msgstr ""
"Els registres de transaccions (donació/venda) s’han conservat íntegrament — "
"els registres financers estan subjectes a una obligació legal de conservació "
"i estan exempts de supressió segons l’art. 17(3)(b) del RGPD."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:766
msgid ""
"Agnosis is a federated art-publishing plugin. The following is a starting "
"point for describing what it collects — review and adapt it to your site's "
"actual configuration before publishing."
msgstr ""
"Agnosis és un connector federat de publicació artística. El text següent és "
"un punt de partida per descriure què recull — revisa’l i adapta’l a la "
"configuració real del teu lloc abans de publicar-lo."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:767
msgid "What personal data we collect and why"
msgstr "Quines dades personals recopilem i per què"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:768
msgid ""
"When you apply to join, we store your email address, display name, "
"biography, statement, and portfolio link to run the community vouching "
"process. When you email us artwork, a biography, or an event, the content of "
"that email (including your address) is stored while it is processed and "
"reviewed. When you subscribe to our newsletter or message an artist through "
"their contact form, we store your email address (and, for contact messages, "
"your IP address) to deliver that message or send you future issues."
msgstr ""
"Quan et presentes per unir-te, emmagatzemem la teva adreça electrònica, nom "
"visible, biografia, declaració i enllaç del portafolis per gestionar el "
"procés d’avals de la comunitat. Quan ens envies obres, una biografia o un "
"esdeveniment per correu electrònic, el contingut d’aquest correu (inclosa la "
"teva adreça) s’emmagatzema mentre es processa i es revisa. Quan et subscrius "
"al nostre butlletí o envies un missatge a un artista a través del seu "
"formulari de contacte, emmagatzemem la teva adreça electrònica (i, en el cas "
"dels missatges de contacte, també la teva adreça IP) per lliurar aquest "
"missatge o enviar-te futurs números."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:769
msgid "Who we share it with"
msgstr "Amb qui ho compartim"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:770
msgid ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."
msgstr ""
"Submitted artwork descriptions and images may be sent to a third-party AI "
"provider (OpenAI or Anthropic, depending on this site's configuration) to "
"help write publication text and enhance images. If this site instead uses "
"WordPress's own built-in AI Client (configured under Settings → Connectors), "
"submitted content is sent to whichever AI service that connector points to "
"instead. Approved posts are also broadcast publicly over ActivityPub (the "
"Fediverse) as part of this plugin's core federation feature."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:771
msgid "How long we retain your data"
msgstr "Durant quant de temps conservem les teves dades"

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:772
msgid ""
"Retention varies by data type; see this site's administrator for specifics. "
"You can request a copy of, or the erasure of, the personal data described "
"above at any time using this site's standard WordPress data request tools."
msgstr ""
"La conservació varia segons el tipus de dada; consulta’n els detalls amb "
"l’administrador d’aquest lloc. Pots sol·licitar en qualsevol moment una "
"còpia o l’esborrat de les dades personals descrites més amunt mitjançant les "
"eines estàndard de WordPress per a sol·licituds de dades d’aquest lloc."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:800
msgid ""
"Submitted text and images may be processed by a third-party AI provider. "
"Approved posts are published publicly and shared across the Fediverse — this "
"cannot be fully undone later."
msgstr ""
"El text i les imatges enviats es poden processar mitjançant un proveïdor "
"extern d’IA. Les publicacions aprovades es publiquen públicament i es "
"comparteixen a tot el Fediverse — això no es pot desfer completament després."

#: includes/Core/Privacy.php:801
msgid ""
"Your message may be reviewed by an automated content filter before being "
"sent to the artist."
msgstr ""
"El teu missatge pot ser revisat per un filtre automàtic de contingut abans "
"d’enviar-se a l’artista."

