"Thanks for signing up! Confirm your email address to start receiving the "
"newsletter."
msgstr ""
"Gràcies per registrar-te! Confirma la teva adreça electrònica per començar a "
"rebre el butlletí."

#: includes/Newsletter/Subscription.php:137
#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:204
