msgstr "Confirma la subscripció"

#: includes/Newsletter/Subscription.php:143
msgid ""
"If you didn't request this, simply ignore this email — you will not be "
"subscribed."
msgstr ""
"Si no ho has sol·licitat, simplement ignora aquest correu — no se't "
"subscriurà."

#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:88
msgid "Artists are automatically subscribed — there is nothing to confirm."
msgstr "Els artistes se subscriuen automàticament — no cal confirmar res."

#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:156
msgid "Subscription confirmed"
msgstr "Subscripció confirmada"

#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:156
