msgstr "No s'ha trobat el compte."

#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:186
msgid ""
"You will no longer receive the artist newsletter. You can re-subscribe any "
"time from your submissions page."
msgstr ""
"Ja no rebràs el butlletí d'artista. Pots tornar-te a subscriure en qualsevol "
"moment des de la teva pàgina d'enviaments."

#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:202
msgid "Confirm your subscription?"
msgstr "Confirmes la teva subscripció?"

#: includes/Newsletter/SubscriptionConfirm.php:203
