#: blocks/breadcrumb-icon-link/block.json
msgctxt "block title"
msgid "Breadcrumb Icon Link"
msgstr "Enllaç d'icona de breadcrumb"

#: blocks/breadcrumb-icon-link/block.json
msgctxt "block description"
msgid ""
"A single icon-only link (Biography, Events, or a Contact popover) to/about "
"the current artist, or a plain-text Language badge showing their native "
"language as a two-letter code. Renders nothing if there's nothing to show "
"(no biography/events yet, the artist has turned contact off, or no native "
"language is set), or off an artist subdomain."
msgstr ""
"Un únic enllaç només amb icona (Biografia, Esdeveniments o un popover de "
"contacte) cap a/sobre l'artista actual, o una insígnia d'idioma en text pla "
"que mostra el seu idioma nadiu com a codi de dues lletres. No mostra res si "
"no hi ha res per mostrar (encara no hi ha biografia/esdeveniments, l'artista "
"ha desactivat el contacte o no hi ha cap idioma nadiu definit), o fora d'un "
"subdomini d'artista."

